Package: SimpleSurvival
Type: Package
Title: Performs simple tasks for survival analysis
Version: 0.0.0
Author: Alberto Alvarez-Iglesias
Maintainer: Alberto Alvarez-Iglesias <alberto.alvarez-iglesias@nuigalway.ie>
Description: Performs some simple tasks for the analysis of time to event data. These include:
    - Kaplan-Meier estimation of the suvivor function 
    - Log-Rank test
    - Cox proportional hazard models (with stratification and proportional hazards diagnostics)
    - Survival trees using conditional independence approach.
    Note that Cox models cannot include interation terms at the moment (this will be implemented in future versions) 
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: jmvcore (>= 0.8.5), R6, survival, ggfortify, survminer, tidyverse, broom, party
